26 shall be used by the Department of Revenue to defray the costs incurred
27 to administer the act, and (e) under section 77-3,124.
28 (c) Any money in the Department of Revenue Enforcement Fund
29 available for investment shall be invested by the state investment
30 officer pursuant to the Nebraska Capital Expansion Act and the Nebraska
31 State Funds Investment Act. Beginning October 1, 2024, any investment
-63-

ER133 ER133
